page.title: 15LARAS DAY CONT.
page.content: I walk to school and on my way meet my best friend ELAINE LENNOX.I normally look for insects which is one of my hobbies.I spotted a worm, a spider, a ladybird and a beetle.It was Monday and during music the class played pop/records.For lunch I ate sausages,chips,beans,toffee/cake and custard.All the girls played handstands at lunch/time.At school we did maths and English finishing off our day with physical education.When I came home at 4o/clock I took GUY for a walk to buy some sweets.For tea I ate beef olives and herb potatoes with French beans.For seconds I had caramel pudding.At 9.30 I went to the toilet, changed into my night/clothes, brushed my teeth and jumped into my warm bed. I usually read till 10.30 and then fall asleep thinking of my busy day//////////////////////
